title: Dab Stew
content: Dab Stew is an item produced from the passive cooking activity cooking dab stew. The only use for this product is selling it to the head chef at The Delectable Dab. Dab stew is made from Common Dab acquired through passive fishing. Cooking Dab stew takes 10 seconds to cook, uses 0.01 common dab and produces 0.01 dab stew and 2 chef xp for a rate of 720xp per hour at a cost of 3.2 dab per hour.
